metadata.name: PANTHERA TIGRIS
metadata.description:
Art work is tribute to endangered Panthera Tigris. However, loss of habitat due to rapid development, agriculture expansion and widespread hunting, has caused the population to decline to about 3,900 individuals at the turn of the century. 

ORIGINAL ART WORK DETAIL: 
Size 297mm x 210mm 
Medium: Acrylic on Acrylic Paper 360gsm
Color used: Reeves Acrylic
1. Orange-Maranja 
2.Medium Yellow - Amarillo Medio 
3.Brown - Terracotta 
4.Titanium white - Blanko de Titanio 
5. Mars Black - Negro de Marte
